### ============================================================
### SHIFTS & HOLIDAYS — Manual Test Guide
### ============================================================
### วิธีใช้:
###   1. เปิดไฟล์นี้ใน VS Code (REST Client extension) หรือ Rider
###   2. ทำ Step 0 ก่อนเสมอ — copy accessToken ไปวางใน @token
###   3. ทำตามลำดับ Step 1 → Step 2 → ...
### ============================================================

@base = http://localhost:5134
@token = PASTE_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE
@companyId = c89cb0d1-7548-4c1b-a36a-929f094f0b30

### ============================================================
### STEP 0: Login (Admin) → copy accessToken ใส่ @token ด้านบน
### ============================================================

POST {{base}}/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@hrms.com",
  "password": "Admin@1234"
}

###

### ============================================================
### STEP 1: ดู Company ที่มีอยู่ → copy companyId ไปใช้ใน Step 2
### ============================================================

GET {{base}}/v1/companies
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ============================================================
### SHIFT — กะงาน
### ============================================================

### [S1] สร้างกะงานเช้า (แทนที่ companyId ด้วยค่าจริง)
# @name createShift
POST {{base}}/v1/shifts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "companyId": "{{companyId}}",
  "name": "กะเช้า",
  "startTime": "08:00:00",
  "endTime": "17:00:00",
  "gracePeriodMinutes": 15
}

###

### [S2] สร้างกะบ่าย
POST {{base}}/v1/shifts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "companyId": "{{companyId}}",
  "name": "กะบ่าย",
  "startTime": "13:00:00",
  "endTime": "22:00:00",
  "gracePeriodMinutes": 10
}

###

### [S3] ดูรายการกะงานทั้งหมด
GET {{base}}/v1/shifts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### [S4] กรองเฉพาะ company
GET {{base}}/v1/shifts?companyId=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### [S5] ดูกะงานตัวเดียว (แทนที่ {shiftId})
GET {{base}}/v1/shifts/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### [S6] แก้ไขกะงาน (แทนที่ {shiftId})
PUT {{base}}/v1/shifts/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "กะเช้า (ปรับใหม่)",
  "startTime": "07:30:00",
  "endTime": "16:30:00",
  "gracePeriodMinutes": 10,
  "isActive": true
}

###

### [S7] ปิดกะงาน (soft delete)
PATCH {{base}}/v1/shifts/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isActive": false
}

###

### [S8] เปิดกะงานกลับ
PATCH {{base}}/v1/shifts/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isActive": true
}

###

### [S9] ดูรายการรวม inactive ด้วย
GET {{base}}/v1/shifts?includeInactive=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ---- Error cases ----

### [S-ERR1] startTime >= endTime → ต้องได้ 400
POST {{base}}/v1/shifts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "companyId": "{{companyId}}",
  "name": "กะผิดพลาด",
  "startTime": "17:00:00",
  "endTime": "08:00:00",
  "gracePeriodMinutes": 0
}

###

### [S-ERR2] GracePeriodMinutes เกิน 120 → ต้องได้ 400
POST {{base}}/v1/shifts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "companyId": "{{companyId}}",
  "name": "กะเกิน",
  "startTime": "08:00:00",
  "endTime": "17:00:00",
  "gracePeriodMinutes": 150
}

###

### [S-ERR3] ชื่อซ้ำใน company เดียวกัน → ต้องได้ 409
POST {{base}}/v1/shifts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "companyId": "{{companyId}}",
  "name": "กะเช้า",
  "startTime": "08:00:00",
  "endTime": "17:00:00",
  "gracePeriodMinutes": 15
}

###

### ============================================================
### HOLIDAY — วันหยุด
### ============================================================

### [H1] เพิ่มวันหยุดแห่งชาติ (companyId = null)
POST {{base}}/v1/holidays
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "companyId": null,
  "name": "วันปีใหม่",
  "date": "2026-01-01"
}

###

### [H2] เพิ่มวันหยุดแห่งชาติเพิ่มเติม
POST {{base}}/v1/holidays
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "companyId": null,
  "name": "วันสงกรานต์",
  "date": "2026-04-13"
}

###

### [H3] เพิ่มวันหยุดเฉพาะ company
POST {{base}}/v1/holidays
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "companyId": "{{companyId}}",
  "name": "วันก่อตั้งบริษัท",
  "date": "2026-03-15"
}

###

### [H4] ดูวันหยุดปี 2026 (ทุก role ดูได้)
GET {{base}}/v1/holidays?year=2026
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### [H5] กรองเฉพาะ company
GET {{base}}/v1/holidays?year=2026&companyId=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### [H6] แก้ไขวันหยุด (แทนที่ {holidayId})
PUT {{base}}/v1/holidays/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "วันปีใหม่ (แก้ไข)",
  "date": "2026-01-01",
  "isActive": true
}

###

### [H7] ปิดวันหยุด (soft delete)
PATCH {{base}}/v1/holidays/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isActive": false
}

###

### [H8] ดูรวม inactive
GET {{base}}/v1/holidays?year=2026&includeInactive=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ---- Error cases ----

### [H-ERR1] วันซ้ำ scope เดียวกัน → ต้องได้ 409
POST {{base}}/v1/holidays
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "companyId": null,
  "name": "วันปีใหม่ซ้ำ",
  "date": "2026-01-01"
}

###
